<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a17Jul1928"><font color="red">17 July 1928</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver): Stifled by heat after having been held up for an hour in the A.L.P.s by a thunderstorm, which stopped our electric train we are here when H.C.E. he cthunders everymoment. </div>
